# Go build outputs
# bin/ is TRACKED: the plugin ships per-arch binaries + a uname launcher (a
# "source":"./" marketplace install only gets tracked files). Staged via the
# kit's stage-binaries; do not re-gitignore.
dist/
*.exe
*.test
*.out

# ask state (per-user, per-machine)
.ask/

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
.act/index.db

# Agent worktrees (created by Claude orchestrator)
.claude/
.act/

# Build-side agent orientation (private; not shipped in public clones — see act-e85f74).
# Kept locally for development agents; use-facing docs live in README.md / SKILL.md.
/CLAUDE.md
.claude/settings.local.json

# Scope-review revised drafts pending review (operator-workflow artifact)
*.revised.md

# Internal process/design docs — operator-workflow artifacts, not shipped (kept local).
docs/brief.md
docs/plan-v1.md
docs/design-ask-affordance-and-multi-recipient.md
docs/blocks-hook-design.md
docs/distribution-readiness.md
docs/session-handoff.md
